CVSId: $Id: TODO,v 1.4 2001/01/12 08:58:33 exupery Exp $

* As of version 1.0h

+ get rid of \myitem{}{} to use a more standard way of modifying bullets
+ a graphical modeller for easily devising new Prosper styles (in [incr Tcl])
+ macro \forSlides{x-y} for displaying material on slides x, x+1, ..., y 
+ add control on parameters for macros \fromSlide,....
+ option to add automatically buttons on all slides to navigate through the
  logical slides (vs. overlays).
+ offer a `letter' option for styles.